description: Deletes a launch template. Deleting a launch template deletes all of its versions.

parameters.name: LaunchTemplateId
parameters.description: The ID of the launch template. You must specify either the launch template ID or the launch template name, but not both.

parameters.name: LaunchTemplateName
parameters.description: The name of the launch template. You must specify either the launch template ID or the launch template name, but not both.

nested_items.name: LaunchTemplateId
nested_items.description: The ID of the launch template.

nested_items.name: LaunchTemplateName
nested_items.description: The name of the launch template.

nested_items.name: CreateTime
nested_items.description: The time launch template was created.

nested_items.name: CreatedBy
nested_items.description: The principal that created the launch template.

nested_items.name: DefaultVersionNumber
nested_items.description: The version number of the default version of the launch template.

nested_items.name: LatestVersionNumber
nested_items.description: The version number of the latest version of the launch template.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: The tags for the launch template.

nested_items.name: Managed
nested_items.description: If true, the resource is managed by a service provider.

nested_items.name: Principal
nested_items.description: If managed is true, then the principal is returned. The principal is the service provider that manages the resource.
